  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate acute and long-term safety and effectiveness of Left atrial
      appendage occlusion (LAA)with the AtriCure LAA Occlusion System. This device will be applied
      in patients with atrial fibrillation (AF), paroxysmal, persistent and permanent, undergoing
      cardiac surgery with a concomitant Maze/Ablation procedure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
